import weather_wish_icon from '../assets/icons/weather_wish_icon.png'

const arrayProjects = [
    {
        image: weather_wish_icon, 
        name: 'Weather Wish', 
        description: 'Website where you can find out in detail the weather forecast for any location on the planet. There is an hourly forecast, there is one for 16 days ahead.', 
        skills: 'JavaScript, React.js, React Router, API',
        gitHubLink: 'https://github.com/Maksym711/weather',
        siteLink: 'https://weatherwish.netlify.app',
    }
    
]

export default arrayProjects
